comments.body:
Swapping out 
{code}
touchEnabled:"true"
{code} 
with
{code}
touchEnabled:true
{code}
fixed this issues.

PR: https://github.com/appcelerator/titanium_mobile/pull/5159

For FR, please run the test case below. It should not crash.
Test case:
{code}
var win = Ti.UI.createWindow({
	backgroundColor: "white"
});

var view = Ti.UI.createView({
	backgroundColor: "blue",
	width: 200,
	height: 200,
	touchEnabled: "true"
});

win.add(view);
win.open();
{code}
